= Making and decorating a chocolate layered cake

:context: layer-cake


This document explains how to make a chocolate layered cake and show how to ice and decorate it.

.Prerequisites

* Ensure that you have the following ingredients. Create ref module with list of stuff.
* Cake decorations of your choice are available.

